trans-unit.source: Represents the parameters for a user name security token.
trans-unit.target: 表示用户名安全令牌的参数。

trans-unit.source: This class is a collection of token properties and methods, and is used in creating security binding elements and tokens.
trans-unit.target: 此类是令牌属性和方法的集合，并可用于创建安全绑定元素和令牌。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The difference between these overloads is where instance property values come from.
trans-unit.target: 这些重载之间的区别是各个实例属性值的来源。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.%23ctor%2A> sets them to their default values.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.%23ctor%2A> 将它们设置为各自的默认值。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.%23ctor%2A> takes them from the instance referenced by the input parameter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.%23ctor%2A> 从输入参数引用的实例中获取它们。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The new instance property values are set to their defaults:
trans-unit.target: 将新实例属性值设置为各自的默认值：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.InclusionMode%2A> is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenInclusionMode.AlwaysToRecipient>.
trans-unit.target: 将 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.InclusionMode%2A> 设置为 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenInclusionMode.AlwaysToRecipient>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.ReferenceStyle%2A> is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenReferenceStyle.Internal>.
trans-unit.target: 将 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.ReferenceStyle%2A> 设置为 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenReferenceStyle.Internal>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.RequireDerivedKeys%2A> is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: 将 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.RequireDerivedKeys%2A> 设置为 `true`。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.Clone%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> methods follow the Core design pattern.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.Clone%2A> 和 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> 方法遵循核心设计模式。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> is an `abstract` class that is overridden by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> 是一个 `abstract` 类，该类由 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> 重写。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> method calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters.CloneCore%2A> 方法调用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.UserNameSecurityTokenParameters.%23ctor%2A> 构造函数。

trans-unit.source: The token.
trans-unit.target: 令牌。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenReferenceStyle" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.Tokens.SecurityTokenReferenceStyle" />。

trans-unit.source: Creates a key identifier clause for a token.
trans-unit.target: 为令牌创建密钥标识符子句。

trans-unit.source: The security key identifier clause.
trans-unit.target: 安全密钥标识符子句。

trans-unit.source: Creates a key identifier clause using the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityToken.CreateKeyIdentifierClause%2A> method, with `referenceStyle` as a generic parameter.
trans-unit.target: 使用 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityToken.CreateKeyIdentifierClause%2A> 方法创建密钥标识符子句，并将 `referenceStyle` 作为泛型参数。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="token" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="token" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="referenceStyle" /> is not <see langword="External" /> or <see langword="Internal" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="referenceStyle" /> 不是 <see langword="External" /> 或 <see langword="Internal" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the token has an asymmetric key.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示令牌是否具有非对称密钥。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the token has an asymmetric key; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果该令牌具有非对称密钥，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 始终返回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Asymmetric keys are used in public-key cryptography, which uses two keys, a public key and a private key, which are related mathematically.
trans-unit.target: 非对称密钥用于公钥加密，公钥加密使用两个密钥，即在数学上相关的一个公钥和一个私钥。

trans-unit.source: The public key is distributed widely, but the private key is kept secret.
trans-unit.target: 公钥可广泛分发，私钥则保密。

trans-unit.source: In public-key cryptography, there is no need to exchange a common key.
trans-unit.target: 在公钥加密中，无需交换公共密钥。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement" />。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a security token requirement.
trans-unit.target: 初始化安全令牌需求。

trans-unit.source: The following properties of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement> are initialized:
trans-unit.target: 已初始化 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement> 的下列属性：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement.TokenType%2A> = <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenTypes.UserName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement.TokenType%2A> = <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenTypes.UserName%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement.RequireCryptographicToken%2A> = `true`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenRequirement.RequireCryptographicToken%2A> = `true`。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the token supports client authentication.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示令牌是否支持客户端身份验证。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the token supports client authentication; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果该令牌支持客户端身份验证，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always returns <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 始终返回 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the token supports a Windows identity for authentication.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示令牌是否支持 Windows 标识的身份验证。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the token supports a Windows identity for authentication; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果该令牌支持 Windows 标识的身份验证，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always returns <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 始终返回 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the token supports server authentication.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示令牌是否支持服务器身份验证。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the token supports server authentication; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果该令牌支持服务器身份验证，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Always returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 始终返回 <see langword="false" />。
